            "title": "艾美疫苗mRNA RSV疫苗在美申報臨床 今早股價逆市曾漲逾10%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">艾美疫苗(06660)今早公布，旗下mRNA RSV疫苗已在美國申報臨床；該股應聲炒上，一度逆市漲逾10%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"公司官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20240304_FI_艾美疫苗_source-web_官網_1200.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"公司官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20240304_FI_艾美疫苗_source-web_官網_1200.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">公司官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該股今早最高曾見6.09元；截至約上午10時50分報5.85元，升幅已收窄至5.79%，暫時成交已達2350萬元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該公司今早發通告，表示旗下mRNA RSV(呼吸道合胞病毒)疫苗已於近日向美國食品和藥品監督管理局(FDA)申報臨床。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">通告指出，在臨床前動物試驗中，第三方檢測單位的檢測結果顯示：艾美疫苗的mRNA RSV疫苗特異性IgG抗體滴度、真病毒中和抗體效價、特異性T細胞免疫，均顯著高於國際上市的mRNA RSV對照疫苗。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14683455-%e8%89%be%e7%be%8e%e7%96%ab%e8%8b%97mrna-rsv%e7%96%ab%e8%8b%97%e5%9c%a8%e7%be%8e%e7%94%b3%e5%a0%b1%e8%87%a8%e5%ba%8a-%e4%bb%8a%e6%97%a9%e8%82%a1%e5%83%b9%e9%80%86%e5%b8%82%e6%9b%be%e6%bc%b2%e9%80%be10",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/06660-Web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-05 10:55:26",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
